#, fuzzy
msgid "https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli[Azure CLI Installed]"
msgstr "link:https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli[已安装 Azure CLI]"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide walks you through running a Maven project that can deploy an HTTP Trigger Azure Function class.\n"
"This function class injects a CDI bean service that generates a greeting message that is passed back\n"
"to the client."
msgstr "本指南将引导您运行一个 Maven 项目，该项目可部署一个基于 HTTP 触发器的 Azure Function 类。该函数类会注入一个 CDI Bean 服务，该服务会生成一条问候消息并将其返回给客户端。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Creating the Maven/Gradle Project"
msgstr "创建 Maven/Gradle 项目"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "First, we need a new project. Create a new project with the following command:"
msgstr "首先，我们需要一个新项目。使用以下命令创建一个新项目："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This command generates a project structure importing the Quarkus Azure Functions HTTP extension.\n"
"It includes an example."
msgstr "该命令会生成一个项目结构，其中导入了 Quarkus Azure Functions HTTP 扩展。该项目包含一个示例。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Examining the project"
msgstr "项目审查"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you open the `pom.xml` or `build.gradle` build file of the generated project, you'll see that\n"
"the project is similar to any other Quarkus project.\n"
"The `quarkus-azure-functions` extension is the integration point between\n"
"Quarkus and Azure Functions. It registers callbacks with the Azure Functions runtime to bootstrap\n"
"Quarkus and to set up Quarkus/ArC as the function factory for your function classes."
msgstr "如果您打开生成的项目的 `pom.xml` 或 `build.gradle` 构建文件，会发现该项目与其他任何 Quarkus 项目类似。 `quarkus-azure-functions` 扩展是 Quarkus 与 Azure Functions 之间的集成点。它向 Azure Functions 运行时注册回调，以初始化 Quarkus，并将 Quarkus/ArC 设置为函数类的函数工厂。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The current implementation of the `quarkus-azure-functions` extension no longer requires the\n"
"`azure-functions-maven-plugin` or Gradle equivalent. Local development and Azure Functions packaging and\n"
"deployment is now all done by Quarkus."
msgstr "`quarkus-azure-functions` 扩展的当前实现已不再需要 `azure-functions-maven-plugin` 或 Gradle 的等效插件。本地开发以及 Azure Functions 的打包和部署现均由 Quarkus 完成。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Build configuration is now all within `application.properties`. The only required configuration switch\n"
"is `quarkus.azure-functions.app-name`."
msgstr "构建配置现已全部包含在 `application.properties` 文件中。唯一必需的配置开关是 `quarkus.azure-functions.app-name` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Azure Deployment Descriptors"
msgstr "Azure 部署描述符"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Azure Functions `host.json` deployment descriptor is automatically\n"
"generated, but if you need to override it, declare it in the root directory of the project and\n"
"rerun the build when you are ready."
msgstr "Azure Functions 的 `host.json` 部署描述符是自动生成的，但如果您需要覆盖它，请在项目的根目录中声明该文件，并在准备就绪后重新运行构建。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus dev mode"
msgstr "Quarkus 开发模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus dev mode does not work currently with Azure Functions."
msgstr "Quarkus 开发模式目前无法与 Azure Functions 配合使用。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run locally in Azure Functions local environment"
msgstr "在 Azure Functions 本地环境中运行"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you want to try your app with a local Azure Functions environment, you can\n"
"use this command:"
msgstr "如果您想在本地 Azure Functions 环境中测试您的应用，可以使用以下命令："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gradle is a bit quirky with process management, so you need the `--no-daemon` switch, or control-c will not\n"
"destroy the process cleanly, and you'll have open ports."
msgstr "Gradle 在进程管理方面有些特殊，因此你需要使用 `--no-daemon` 参数，否则按下 Ctrl+C 无法干净地终止进程，导致端口保持打开状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You must have the https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools]\n"
"installed for this to work."
msgstr "要使此功能正常工作，您必须已安装 link:https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The URL to access the example would be:"
msgstr "访问该示例的 URL 如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://localhost:8081/HttpExample?name=Bill"
msgstr "https://localhost:8081/HttpExample?name=Bill"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Integration Testing"
msgstr "Quarkus 集成测试"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can implement integration tests using `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` functionality.  When these\n"
"integration tests run, the local Azure Functions environment will be spun up for the duration of integration testing."
msgstr "您可以使用 `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` 功能来实现集成测试。当这些集成测试运行时，系统会在集成测试期间启动本地 Azure Functions 环境。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Maven"
msgstr "Maven"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gradle"
msgstr "Gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make sure any integration tests you execute with Maven use the `*IT.java` file pattern so that regular builds do not execute\n"
"the test."
msgstr "请确保使用 Maven 执行的任何集成测试都采用 `*IT.java` 的文件命名模式，以免常规构建过程中执行该测试。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make sure any integration tests you execute with Gradle are located within `src/integrationTest/java`. Integration\n"
"tests that exist in `src/test` will run with normal build and fail."
msgstr "请确保使用 Gradle 执行的任何集成测试都位于 `src/integrationTest/java` 目录下。位于 `src/test` 目录下的集成测试会在常规构建过程中运行，并导致构建失败。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Login to Azure"
msgstr "登录 Azure"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To be able to deploy your application to Azure, log in to Azure:"
msgstr "要将应用程序部署到 Azure，请登录 Azure："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Deploy to Azure"
msgstr "部署到 Azure"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-azure-functions` extension handles all the work to deploy to Azure. By default,\n"
"Quarkus will use the Azure CLI in the background to authenticate and deploy to Azure. If you have\n"
"multiple subscriptions associated with your account, you must set the `quarkus.azure-functions.subscription-id`\n"
"property in your `application.properties` file to the subscription you want to use.\n"
"For other authentication mechanisms and deployment options, see our config properties <<#configuration-reference>>."
msgstr "`quarkus-azure-functions` 扩展负责处理所有部署到 Azure 的工作。默认情况下，Quarkus 会在后台使用 Azure CLI 进行身份验证并部署到 Azure。 如果您的账户关联了多个订阅，则必须在 `application.properties` 文件中将 `quarkus.azure-functions.subscription-id` 属性设置为您要使用的订阅。有关其他身份验证机制和部署选项，请参阅我们的配置属性文档： <<configuration-reference>> 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To deploy your application, after you built your project, execute:"
msgstr "要部署您的应用程序，请在构建项目后执行以下命令："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Gradle, you must use the `--info` switch to see this output."
msgstr "对于 Gradle，必须使用 `--info` 选项才能看到此输出。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If deployment is a success, Quarkus will output the endpoint URL of the example function to the console:"
msgstr "如果部署成功，Quarkus 会将示例函数的端点 URL 输出到控制台："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/azure-functions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The URL to access the service would be: `https://{appName}.azurewebsites.net/api/HttpExample`"
msgstr "访问该服务的 URL 如下： `https://{appName}.azurewebsites.net/api/HttpExample`"

